org.apache.taverna.server.master.notification.atom

Class AtomFeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.server.master.notification.atom.AtomFeed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UriBuilderFactory, TavernaServerREST.EventFeed, org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware

    public class AtomFeed
extends Object
implements TavernaServerREST.EventFeed, UriBuilderFactory, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware
    Simple REST handler that allows an Atom feed to be served up of events generated by workflow runs.

    Donal Fellows

        public static final String PREFERRED_URI_PARAM
